name: The Trees and The Life #006-Biduk
description:
No one ever heard it before, especially for me. It's the road less traveled. This cape holds one of the unique natural phenomena ever when salt and fresh water meet. Home to hectares of mangrove forest also. It's a nursery for a lot of species. It also protects the coastal from abrasion, like Yggdrasil it protects the realm around it.

The Trees and The Life is a 10-Photo-Based-NFT Collection made by Danar Tri Atmojo. As the first-ever collection made, Danar dedicated these NFT's to mother nature as we move towards the new era of digitalization using Tezos blockchain as #CleanNFTs.
